Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:05.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962.182,963.091)}海绵宝宝  之
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:10.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.364,1030.727)}过不完的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:15.19,注释,,0,0,0,,翻译  1440kHz
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,﻿到蟹堡王去上班
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm off to work at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.81,0:00:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做蟹黄堡扯扯淡
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.81,0:00:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fryin' up patties and blabbity bla-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,654)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.52,0:00:16.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒新鲜
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.52,0:00:16.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's new
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把车停到这也太怪了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strange place to park a car
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.13,0:00:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是干嘛的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.13,0:00:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在浪费我的宝贝二氧化碳
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wastin' me precious carbon dioxide
Dialogue: 2,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二氧化碳
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carbon dioxide?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.99,0:00:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在把它排放到大气层  小子
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.99,0:00:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pumpin' it into the atmosphere, boy
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全球气候变暖了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks to global warmin'
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说气温很快就会飞涨
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the temperature will soon go through the roof
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能过上过不完的夏天了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we'll have an endless summer
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.91,0:00:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛想要个过不完的夏天  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you want an endless summer, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能开展我最新的赚钱大计
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I can open me latest money-makin' venture
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡泳池
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krusty Pool
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是冬季运动怎么办  蟹老板
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, what about winter sports, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管冬季了  小子
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget winter, boy
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点可是晒日光浴  冲浪
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're talkin' sun tannin', hangin' 10
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有游泳一整年
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and swimmin' all year long
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过不完的夏天听着确实好玩
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The endless summer does sound fun
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能赚大钱
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And profitable
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又好玩又能赚大钱
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun and profitable
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大生意又成功了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big business does it again
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能马上就过上过不完的夏天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wish it could be the endless summer right now
Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.93,0:01:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雨伞三块钱  先生
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.93,0:01:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Umbrellars are three dollars, sir
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真实惠
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a bargain
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.47,0:01:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你五块
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.47,0:01:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give ya five
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.52,0:01:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.52,0:01:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.25,0:01:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面突然就热起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.25,0:01:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It suddenly got very warm in here
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.54,0:01:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁调高了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.54,0:01:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who turned up the--
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.62,0:01:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暖气
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.62,0:01:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,heat?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你干什么
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are ya doin'?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.17,0:01:26.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是再往火堆里丢个轮胎进去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.17,0:01:26.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just throwin' another tire on the fire
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.11,0:01:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,促进全球气候变暖  蟹老板
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.11,0:01:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for global warming, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.51,0:01:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.51,0:01:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.95,0:01:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.95,0:01:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村都过来解暑了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The entire town is heading this way to cool off
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是要来付我钱了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean pay off
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给泳池装水啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fill the pool, fill the pool
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.21,0:01:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你们的钱都准备好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.21,0:01:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have your money ready, folks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:43.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,448)}游泳
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,队伍从这里开始排
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The line starts here
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家这是要去哪
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's everybody goin'?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要搬去北方
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all moving north
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里再也没法住了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't live here anymore
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快热死了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too hot
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我客人都搬去气候更凉快的地方了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All me customers have moved to cooler climates
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.67,0:01:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐观点看嘛  蟹老板
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.67,0:01:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.82,0:02:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池不会有人来排队了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.82,0:02:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There won't be a line to go in the pool
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮来了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
